hurting her again?

00:03:42.055 --> 00:03:45.058 align:middle
Now that you mention it, she has
been working later than usual.

00:03:45.141 --> 00:03:47.477 align:middle
Our sales team is talented,
but we work harder.

00:03:47.560 --> 00:03:49.771 align:middle
