00:03:49.854 --> 00:03:52.023 align:middle
Well, there is something
else I noticed.

00:03:52.107 --> 00:03:53.108 align:middle
Great! What is it?

00:03:53.191 --> 00:03:55.068 align:middle
She has really
bad posture in general.

00:03:55.151 --> 00:03:57.654 align:middle
What does that have to do
with her lower back hurting?

00:03:57.737 --> 00:03:59.948 align:middle
Ah, jeez. Lemme
break it down for you:

00:04:00.031 --> 00:04:01.324 align:middle
these humans
can strain their backs

00:04:01.408 --> 00:04:02.992 align:middle
by hunching over
their keyboards.

00:04:03.076 --> 00:04:04.160 align:middle
They can?!

00:04:04.244 --> 00:04:06.162 align:middle
She should probably
buy a new chair.

00:04:06.246 --> 00:04:07.580 align:middle
What?

00:04:07.664 --> 00:04:09.374 align:middle
She's been using the same
old offensive office chair

00:04:09.457 --> 00:04:11.668 align:middle
for years now. I've
been saying it's about time

00:04:11.751 --> 00:04:14.129 align:middle
for her to treat herself
to a fancy upgrade.

00:04:14.212 --> 00:04:15.964 align:middle
She says she doesn't
want to pay for one.

00:04:16.047 --> 00:04:17.382 align:middle
[TOHRU]
Are they expensive?

00:04:17.465 --> 00:04:19.801 align:middle
Is Miss Kobayashi one of those
humans who buy multiples

00:04:19.884 --> 00:04:22.762 align:middle
of products because she thinks
it makes them cheaper?

00:04:22.846 --> 00:04:26.182 align:middle
Yep. She also buys well
liquor and nurses it all night.

00:04:26.266 --> 00:04:29.477 align:middle
If she would eat my tail,
she wouldn't have any back pain.

00:04:29.561 --> 00:04:30.895 align:middle
Whatever.
[sighs]

00:04:30.979 --> 00:04:32.731 align:middle
Yeah, but then
her stomach would hurt.

00:04:32.814 --> 00:04:34.524 align:middle
