00:04:38.737 --> 00:04:41.364 align:middle
That's, uh...
maybe not a good idea.

00:04:41.448 --> 00:04:42.907 align:middle
[TOHRU]
Hmm?

00:04:42.991 --> 00:04:46.161 align:middle
Have you heard the story of
eating the flesh of the dead?

00:04:46.244 --> 00:04:48.663 align:middle
